            _angular_core__WEBPACK_IMPORTED_MODULE_0__["ɵɵtext"](27, " We use the Service to allow you to connect your bank account. Connecting your bank account helps us better support your requested payments, including by verifying your bank account and accelerating your payments where possible. ");
